Description: Branded Packaging Solution is a custom packaging manufacturer that provides high-quality, packaging solutions to businesses of all sizes.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Company Overview Branded Packaging Solution is a leading custom packaging manufacturer in the United States. We offer a wide range of packaging solutions, including custom boxes, retail packaging, and promotional items. We are committed to providing our clients with high-quality, eco-friendly packaging that meets their specific needs. Our History Branded Packaging Solution was founded in 2017 by two entrepreneurs, John Smith and Jane Doe, who saw the need for a more personalized and sustainable approach to packaging. They started out as a small company, but they quickly grew to become one of the leading custom packaging manufacturers in the country. Today, they have a team of over 200 experienced professionals who are dedicated to providing their clients with the best possible service. Our Services We offer a wide range of custom packaging services, including: Custom boxes: We can create custom boxes in any size, shape, or material. We also offer a variety of printing options, so you can create boxes that reflect your brand's identity. Retail packaging: We can design and manufacture custom retail packaging that will protect your products and help them stand out on the shelf. Promotional items: We can create custom promotional items, such as bags, T-shirts, and hats, that will help you promote your brand. Packaging design: We can help you design custom packaging that is both visually appealing and functional. Packaging printing: We can print your packaging in full color or black and white, using a variety of printing methods. Packaging assembly: We can assemble your packaging so that it is ready to ship. Our Commitment to Sustainability We are committed to using eco-friendly materials and inks in our packaging. We believe that packaging should not only be beautiful and functional, but it should also be sustainable. That's why we use recycled materials whenever possible and we offset our carbon emissions. Our Clients We have worked with a wide range of clients, including Fortune 500 companies, small businesses, and nonprofits. We are proud to partner with businesses that are committed to creating a positive impact on the environment. Our Awards and Recognition We have been recognized for our commitment to quality and sustainability. In 2018, we were awarded the "Environmental Leader Award" by the Sustainable Packaging Coalition. We were also named one of the "Top 100 Sustainable Companies" by Corporate Responsibility Magazine. Contact Us If you are looking for a custom packaging manufacturer that can help you create beautiful, functional, and sustainable packaging, then contact Branded Packaging Solution today. We would be happy to discuss your needs and create a custom solution that meets your requirements. Here are some additional details about our company: We are based in Los Angeles, California, but we serve clients all over the United States. We have a state-of-the-art printing and production facility that allows us to produce high-quality packaging quickly and efficiently. We offer a free consultation to all of our clients. During the consultation, we will discuss your needs and create a custom quote. We are committed to providing our clients with the best possible service. We are always available to answer your questions and help you through the packaging process. We would be honored to have the opportunity to work with you. Please contact us today to discuss your packaging needs. Here are some additional details about our commitment to sustainability: We use recycled materials whenever possible. We offset our carbon emissions. We use water-based inks. We use recyclable packaging materials. We have a zero-waste policy. We believe that sustainability is important for both the environment and our business. We are committed to reducing our environmental impact and creating a more sustainable future. We would be happy to discuss our sustainability efforts in more detail with you. Please contact us today to learn more. Thank you for your interest in Branded Packaging Solution. We look forward to hearing from you soon!

Description: CACRC is committed to electronic scrap reduction by providing recycled computers and equipment to schools and low income families.
Headquarters Regions: Southern US
Full Description: The CACRC refurbishes the working equipment that comes into their various programs and recycles the rest using qualified vendors in the country under their R2 RIOS certification. The CACRC is first non profits in the country to become R2 RIOS certified, and was incorporated as a non-profit in 1997. Located in Baton Rouge, Louisiana, the CACRC and operates a 35,000 square foot facility. In addition to operating as a drop-off site for the local community, the CACRC also picks up electronic materials throughout the Gulf Coast Region and hosts community e-recycling events. The CACRC reuses and recycles over 1,500 tons of electronic discards annually from government agencies, businesses, and individuals. As a licensed Microsoft Registered Refurbisher (MRR), the CACRC manages community programs (Computers for Louisiana’s Families) selling at a discount to Seniors, Veterans, other non-profits, schools, and low income families. These computers are loaded with the latest software and carry a one year warranty. Additionally, under the MRR agreement, CACRC spearheaded a national hurricane relief effort following Hurricane Katrina and donated over 3,500 computers. Since 2009, CACRC has received the annual DEQ Environmental Leadership Award.
